description: Trickster Company designs, together with Natives Outdoors to empower Indigenous communities, bring their favorite upstream swimmers to life in this latest collaboration. Their Sockeye Season Graphic Short Sleeve Tee combines the moisture management, temperature regulation, and odor resistance of Merino with the durability and quick dry time of recycled polyester for a comfortable tee that’s always ready to get out there.
name: Smartwool Sockseye Season Graphic SS Tee - Unisex

specs.value: 56% Merino Wool, 44% Recycled Polyester - Exclusive of Decoration
